                     <interp inst="t17971025-2-off7" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17971025-2-off7" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17971025-2-cd8" type="crimeDate">6th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17971025-2-off7 t17971025-2-cd8"></join>, two pieces of printed cotton, containing fifty-six yards, value 4l. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17971025-2-victim60" type="victimName">
                        Robert 
                        Waithman
                     <interp inst="t17971025-2-victim60" type="surname" value="Waithman"></interp>
